[normal]Supplementary evidence – safety at level crossing[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]Please find below further information requested as part of your inquiry into level crossing safety. 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]1. [bold]How will the £109 million be spent over CP5? What will go on upgrades, closures etc?[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]I provide further clarification of what we are expecting from Network Rail in the next control period below:  
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]All three tables below come from the supporting information provided to ORR by Network Rail during the consultation period, illustrating the case for the additional investment sought by Network Rail. In the context of the determination where Network Rail will be expected to achieve maximum risk reduction, the company will keep the specific deliverables under review and the exact mix might have to flex to meet that.
[normal]&#xa0;
